# Plot PCoA Weighted Unifrac ajustado com variável contínua IL-4
ggplot(merge(wunifrac.pcoa$points, subset(metadados, !is.na(IL4)), by.x = "row.names", by.y = "Sample.id")) + 
  geom_point(aes(x = V1, y = V2, color = IL4), size = 2) + 
  scale_color_gradient(low = "blue", high = "red", name = "IL4") +
  labs(title = "Weighted Unifrac", x = "V1", y = "V2") +
  theme_minimal()
